# Summary
This documentation describes the Amplitude-Leanplum integration that enables syncing user cohorts from Amplitude to Leanplum for targeted marketing campaigns, requiring a paid Amplitude plan, Leanplum account approval, and proper user ID configuration, with step-by-step setup instructions for both platforms and a cohort syncing process.

